%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Vigna%20said%20he%20believed%20that%20companies%20work%20more%20efficiently%20through%20smaller%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20big%20team%20you%20feel%20like%20a%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Bloomberg.%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20small%20team%2C%20you%20are%20a%20person%20that's%20contributing%20one%20way%20or%20another.%20Also%2C%20the%20speed%20of%20learning%20from%20mistakes%20is%20much%20faster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-does-not-understand-ferrari-business-2017-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20responded%20well%20to%20Vigna's%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Journal%2C%20the%20company%20stock%20price%20has%20nearly%20doubled%20since%20Vigna%20took%20control%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFerrari%20also%20plans%20to%20roll%20out%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fferrari-ceo-ev-wont-be-silent-like-tesla-car-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20electric%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Ferrari%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20during%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fferrari-ceo-benedetto-vigna-leads-company-tech-startup-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713671599000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6624871c0dfb1341e9fd5b6f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fferrari-ceo-benedetto-vigna-leads-company-tech-startup-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Benedetto%20Vigna%2C%20Ferrari's%20CEO%20since%202021%2C%20prefers%20a%20flatter%20corporate%20structure%20and%20a%20company%20with%20the%20nim