e%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20annulled%20the%20marriage%20of%20a%20young%20couple%20that%20could%20not%20consummate%20it%20due%20to%20the%20man's%20'relative%20impotency'%2C%20noting%20their%20agony%20of%20frustration%20cannot%20be%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20justices%20Vibha%20Kankanwadi%20and%20S%20G%20Chapalgaonkar%20in%20the%20judgment%20on%20April%2015%20also%20noted%20that%20this%20was%20a%20fit%20case%20to%20help%20%26quot%3Byoung%20sufferers%20of%20marriage%26quot%3B%20who%20could%20not%20connect%20with%20each%20other%20mentally%2C%20emotionally%20or%20physically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2027-year-old%20man%20had%20approached%20the%20bench%20after%20a%20family%20court%20in%20February%202024%20refused%20an%20application%20filed%20by%20his%2026-year-old%20wife%2C%20seeking%20to%20annul%20the%20marriage%20on%20the%20admission%20stage%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20in%20its%20order%20said%20the%20expression%20'relative%20impotency'%20is%20a%20known%20phenomenon%20and%20is%20different%20from%20the%20normal%20impotency%2C%20which%20means%20the%20inability%20to%20copulate%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelative%20impotency%20broadly%20points%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20a%20person%20might%20be%20capable%20of%20having%20intercourse%20but%20incapable%20of%20performing%20it%20with%20the%20spouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20there%20could%20be%20various%20physical%20and%20mental%20causes%20for%20such%20relative%20impotency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20present%20case%2C%20it%20can%20be%20easily%20gathered%20that%20the%20husband%20has%20relative%20impotency%20qua%20(towards)%20the%20wife.%20The%20reason%20for%20non-consummation%20of%20the%20marriage%20is%20this%20apparent%20relative%20impotency%20of%20the%20husband%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20HC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20said%20it%20could%20not%20ignore%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20was%20a%20matter%20concerning%20a%20young%20couple%20who%20faced%20the%20agony%20of%20frustration%20in%20the%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20may%20have%20initially%20blamed%20his%20wife%20for%20non-consummation%20as%20he%20was%20hesitant%20to%20admit%20he%20had%20relative%20impotency%20towards%20her%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20subsequently%2C%20he%20candidly%20admitted%20the%20same%2C%20being%20satisfied%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20would%20not%20put%20lifelong%20stigma%20on%20him.%20The%20relative%20impotency%20is%20somewhat%20different%20than%20the%20general%20notion%20of%20impotency%20and%20the%20acceptance%20of%20relative%20impotency%20would%20not%20brand%20him%20impotent%20in%20general%20parlance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20HC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20got%20married%20in%20March%202023%20but%20separated%20after%2017%20days.%20The%20couple%20said%20their%20marriage%20was%20not%20consummated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20claimed%20the%20man%20had%20declined%20physical%20relations%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20plea%20seeking%20for%20annulment%20of%20marriage%20filed%20before%20the%20family%20court%2C%20the%20woman%20said%20the%20man%20had%20'relative%20impotency'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20they%20could%20not%20connect%20with%20each%20other%20mentally%2C%20emotionally%2C%20or%20physically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20initially%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20before%20the%20family%20court%20stating%20that%20the%20marriage%20was%20not%20consummated%20but%20blamed%20the%20woman%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20submitted%20a%20written%20statement%20admitting%20relative%20impotency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20claimed%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20establish%20physical%20relations%20with%20his%20wife%20but%20otherwise%20he%20was%20normal.%20In%20the%20statement%2C%20he%20said%20he%20did%20not%20want%20any%20stigma%20that%20he%20was%20impotent%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20the%20wife%20filed%20an%20application%20seeking%20the%20family%20court%20to%20decide%20the%20divorce%20plea%20at%20the%20admission%20stage%20itself%20as%20per%20provisions%20of%20the%20Civil%20Procedure%20Code%20instead%20of%20conducting%20a%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20court%2C%20however%2C%20rejected%20the%20application%20claiming%20the%20man%20and%20woman%20had%20raised%20collusive%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HC%20bench%20quashed%20the%20family%20court%20order%20and%20annulled%20the%20marriage%20declaring%20it%20null%20and%20void.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713669480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F85mh9qus_bombay-high-court-website-photo_625x300_20_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyoung-sufferers-bombay-high-court-annuls-marriage-due-to-mans-relative-impotency-5488318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Aurangabad%20bench%20of%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20annulled%20the%20marriage%20of%20a%20young%20couple%20that%20could%20not%20consummate%20it%20due%20to%20the%20man's%20'relative%20impotency'%2C%20noting%20their%20agony%20of%20frustration%20cannot%20be%20ignored.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyoung-sufferers-bombay-high-court-annuls-marriage-due-to-mans-relative-impotency-5488318%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyoung-sufferers-bombay-high-court-annuls-marriage-due-to-mans-relative-impotency-5488318%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyoung-sufferers-bombay-high-court-annuls-marriage-due-to-mans-relative-impotency-5488318%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20Watch%20Dials%20911%2C%20Saves%20New%20York%20Bicyclist's%20Life%20After%20Horrific%20Crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EApple%20Watch%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20life%20saviour%20on%20many%20occasions.%20Many%20reports%20have%20shown%20how%20it%20saved%20lives%20by%20detecting%20abnormalities%20in%20users'%20health%20using%20sensors%20that%20measure%20heart%20rate%2C%20ECG%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%C2%A0In%20one%20such%20recent%20incident%2C%20Apple%20Watch%20saved%20a%20cyclist's%20life%20in%20New%20York%20after%20he%20suffered%20a%20horrific%20bike%20accident.%20The%20incident%20happened%20last%20month%20when%C2%A0Eric%20Zollinger%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20broker%2C%C2%A0was%20riding%20a%20Citi%20Bike%20home%20from%20his%20office%20during%20a%20torrential%20downpour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20commute%20took%20a%20serious%20turn%20when%20he%20encountered%20a%20hidden%20pothole%20submerged%20beneath%20floodwater.%20His%20bike%20hit%20the%20pothole%2C%C2%A0causing%20him%20to%20be%20thrown%20off%20his%20bike%20onto%20the%20pavement.%C2%A0Despite%20sustaining%20injuries%20to%20his%20nose%2C%20face%2C%20and%20knee%2C%20Mr%20Zollinger%20continued%20home%20but%20later%20collapsed%2C%20and%20passed%20out%20in%20his%20bathroom%20where%20he%20hit%20his%20body%20against%20the%20tub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20his%20Apple%20Watch%20detected%20the%20fall%2C%20automatically%20dialled%20911%20and%20alerted%20the%20emergency%20contacts%20of%20his%20location.%20Notably%2C%20the%20smartwatch%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2F108896%5C%22%3Ebuilt-in%20fall%20detection%20function%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20connects%20the%20user%20to%20emergency%20services%20if%20it%20''detects%20a%20hard%20fall.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20next%20thing%20I%20remember%20hearing%20is%2C%20'911%2C%20what's%20your%20emergency%3F''%20Mr%20Zollinger%20said%20while%20recounting%20the%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20visited%20a%20local%20hospital%20to%20get%20an%20evaluation.%20Fortunately%2C%20scans%20showed%20that%20he%20had%20not%20sustained%20any%20broken%20bones%20and%20was%20later%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%C2%A0%C2%A0Zollinger%20praised%20the%20smartwatch's%20quick%20response%20and%20credits%20it%20for%20saving%20his%20life.%20''I%20don't%20know%20how%20things%20would%20have%20gone%20for%20me%20if%20the%20watch%20hadn't%20alerted%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20feel%20very%20fortunate%20and%20grateful%20at%20what%20transpired%20and%20happened%20in%20how%20my%20Apple%20Watch%20helped%20me.%20It's%20a%20very%20clever%20watch.%20Apple%20thinks%20of%20everything%2C''%20Mr%20Zollinger%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmartwatches%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20saving%20many%20lives.%20Last%20year%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20man%20in%20the%20UK%20shared%20how%20a%20smartwatch%20helped%20him%20survive%20a%20heart%20attack.%C2%A0According%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.express.co.uk%2Flife-style%2Fhealth%2F1832321%2Fdad-rushed-to-hospital-heart-attack-sign%5C%22%3EExpress.%20co.%20uk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Paul%20Wapham%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Hockey%20Wales%2C%20was%20on%20his%20morning%20run%20near%20his%20home%20in%20the%20Morriston%20area%20of%20Swansea%20when%20he%20felt%20an%20acute%20pain%20in%20his%20chest.%C2%A0He%20somehow%20managed%20to%20contact%20his%20wife%20through%20his%20watch%2C%20who%20rushed%20him%20to%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Apple%20Watch%20detects%20you%20have%20remained%20motionless%20for%20one%20minute%2C%20an%20emergency%20call%20will%20be%20placed%20automatically%20and%20a%20message%20with%20your%20location%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20your%20emergency%20contacts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713668760000%2C