J%20and%20Kenvue's%20predecessor%20firm%20sold%20their%20talcum-based%20baby%20powder%20knowing%20it%20was%20tainted%20with%20asbestos%2C%20according%20to%20court%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20found%20J%26amp%3BJ%20and%20one%20of%20its%20units%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20remaining%2030%25%20of%20the%20verdict%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20wins%20by%20a%20talc%20plaintiff%20since%20a%20judge%20last%20year%20threw%20out%20the%20bankruptcy%20filing%20of%20a%20J%26amp%3BJ%20unit%20aimed%20at%20forcing%20a%20settlement%20of%20the%20talc%20cases.%20A%20Florida%20jury%20rejected%20similar%20claims%20against%20the%20company%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BJ%20has%20maintained%20that%20its%20talc-based%20products%20don't%20cause%20cancer%20and%20that%20it%20has%20marketed%20its%20baby%20powder%20appropriately%20for%20more%20than%20a%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20of%20Kenvue%2C%20which%20now%20sells%20baby%20powder%2C%20confirmed%20earlier%20this%20month%20it%20no%20longer%20makes%20or%20sells%20a%20talc-based%20version%20of%20the%20product.%20Prior%20to%20the%20spinoff%2C%20J%26amp%3BJ%20said%20it%20would%20take%20talc%20off%20the%20North%20American%20market%20by%202020%20and%20worldwide%20by%20December%202023%20and%20switch%20to%20a%20cornstarch%20replacement.%20It%20cited%20sliding%20sales%20for%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMelissa%20Witt%2C%20a%20Kenvue%20spokeswoman%2C%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20an%20email%20Saturday%20seeking%20comment%20on%20the%20verdict.%20Erik%20Haas%2C%20the%20head%20of%20J%26amp%3BJ's%20in-house%20litigation%20section%2C%20said%20the%20company%20would%20appeal%20the%20jury's%20finding.%20%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20to%20prevail%20as%20we%20typically%20do%20with%20aberrant%20adverse%20verdicts%20that%20have%20no%20basis%20in%20the%20law%20or%20science%20and%20are%20predicated%20on%20clearly%20erroneous%20rulings%20by%20the%20trial%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20Haas%20said%20in%20an%20emailed%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BJ%20is%20among%20a%20host%20of%20big%20drugmakers%20that%20divested%20or%20are%20planning%20to%20divest%20themselves%20of%20lower-margin%2C%20yet%20dependably%20profitable%2C%20consumer%20units%20in%20order%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20high-stakes%20business%20of%20making%20new%20medicines.%20J%26amp%3BJ%20generated%20%2413.2%20billion%20in%20cash%20via%20the%20offering%20of%20Kenvue%20debt%20and%20sale%20of%20its%20shares.%20Kenvue%20is%20now%20home%20to%20popular%20J%26amp%3BJ%20products%20such%20as%20its%20Tylenol%20painkiller%2C%20Listerine%20mouthwash%20and%20the%20new%20cornstarch-based%20version%20of%20baby%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20spinoff%2C%20Kenvue%20secured%20an%20indemnity%20agreement%20from%20J%26amp%3BJ%20to%20cover%20any%20talc%20liability%20that%20arises%20in%20North%20America%2C%20according%20to%20securities%20filings.%20Kenvue%20must%20deal%20with%20talc%20verdicts%20generated%20by%20courts%20outside%20that%20area%2C%20the%20filings%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarcia's%20family%20had%20been%20ready%20to%20go%20to%20trial%20in%202021%20when%20J%26amp%3BJ's%20LTL%20Management%20unit%20filed%20its%20first%20Chapter%2011%20case%20seeking%20to%20foster%20a%20settlement%20of%20all%20current%20and%20future%20talc%20cases%2C%20said%20Jessica%20Dean%2C%20the%20family's%20lawyer.%20Its%20only%20after%20that%20case%20-%20along%20with%20a%20second%20attempt%20to%20use%20the%20bankruptcy%20courts%20to%20corral%20the%20talc%20litigation%20-%20was%20thrown%20out%20that%20the%20family%20was%20able%20to%20have%20a%20jury%20hear%20its%20case%2C%20Dean%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20years%20of%20delay%20caused%20by%20Johnson%20%26amp%3B%20Johnson's%20bad%20faith%20abuse%20of%20the%20bankruptcy%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20family%20is%20grateful%20jurors%20saw%20through%20the%20'deceptions'%20put%20forth%20by%20J%26amp%3BJ%20and%20Kenvue%20about%20whether%20talc%20can%20cause%20cancer%2C%20Dean%20said%20in%20a%20release.%20%26quot%3BThe%20defendants%20knew%20that%20talc%20contains%20asbestos%20impurities%20that%20were%20mined%20and%20put%20in%20the%20bottles%20of%20baby%20powder%20J%26amp%3BJ%20sold%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Florida%20case%2C%20a%20state%20court%20jury%20rejected%20claims%20by%20Patricia%20Matthey's%20family%20that%20her%202016%20ovarian%20cancer%20was%20caused%20by%20using%20baby%20powder%20tainted%20with%20asbestos.%20After%20the%20verdict%2C%20Haas%20said%20the%20company%20was%20vindicated%20by%20the%20panel's%20ruling.%20%26quot%3BThe%20jury%20appropriately%20found%20that%20talc%20is%20safe%2C%20does%20not%20contain%20asbestos%20and%20does%20not%20cause%20cancer%2C%20which%20is%20the%20same%20outcome%20the%20company%20achieved%20in%2016%20of%2017%20ovarian%20cases%20tried%20to%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20Haas%20said%20in%20an%20emailed%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Garcia's%20Chicago%20case%2C%20her%20family%20contends%20the%20plaintiff%20was%20a%20long-time%20user%20of%20J%26amp%3BJ's%20talc-based%20baby%20powder%20and%20used%20the%20product%20on%20her%20children%20and%20grandchildren.%20The%20family%20contends%20J%26amp%3BJ%20was%20aware%20of%20concerns%20about%20asbestos%20in%20its%20talc%20and%20failed%20to%20warn%20consumers.%20Stephanie%20Salcedo%2C%20Garcia's%20daughter%2C%20filed%20the%20case%20on%20behalf%20of%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJ%26amp%3BJ%20knew%20that%20asbestos%20exposure%2C%20including%20asbestos%20exposure%20from%20inhaling%20asbestos-containing%20talc%2C%20can%20and%20does%20cause%20fatal%20diseases%20such%20as%20mesothelioma%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20family%20said%20in%20its%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BJ%20reported%20earnings%20this%20week%2C%20beating%20estimates%20in%20a%20step%20towards%20boosting%20profitability%20after%20the%20spinoff%20of%20Kenvue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chicago%20case%20is%20Salcedo%20v.%20Cyprus%20Amax%20Minerals%2C%20No.020L004505%2C%20Calendar%2C%20J1%2024067608%2C%20Cook%20County%20Circuit%20Court%20(Chicago).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713668220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2Fmdaag3k8_johnson-and-johnson-baby-powder-reuters_625x300_14_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fj-j-kenvue-told-to-pay-45-million-to-baby-powder-users-family-5488282%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Johnson%20%26amp%3B%20Johnson%20and%20Kenvue%20Inc.%20were%20ordered%20to%20pay%20%2445%20million%20to%20the%20family%20of%20an%20Illinois%20woman%20who%20blamed%20the%20companies'%20baby%20powders%20for%20giving%20her%20a%20fatal%20cancer%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fj-j-kenvue-told-to-pay-45-million-to-baby-powder-users-family-5488282%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fj-j-kenvue-told-to-pay-45-million-to-baby-powder-users-family-5488282%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fj-j-kenvue-told-to-pay-45-million-to-baby-powder-users-family-5488282%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%202024%20Playoffs%3A%20What%20Exactly%20Does%20RCB%20Need%20To%20Finish%20In%20Top%204%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20Premier%20League%202024%20is%20nearly%20halfway%20through%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20sides%20have%20found%20the%20right%20combinations%20for%20their%20team.%20Unfortunately%2C%20Royals%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20aren't%20one%20of%20them%20and%20have%20found%20themselves%20struggling%20in%20IPL%202024%20with%20just%20one%20win%20from%20seven%20matches%20so%20far.%20RCB's%20latest%20defeat%20came%20against%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20at%20the%20M.%20Chinnaswamy%20Stadium%20on%20April%2015%20after%20they%20conceded%20287%20runs%20-%20the%20highest-ever%20total%20in%20franchise%20T20%20cricket