20bowling%20unit%20this%20season%20as%20four%20of%20their%20bowlers%20conceded%20more%20than%2050%20runs%20-%20a%20first%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20Indian%20legend%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20currently%20the%20leading%20run-scorer%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20with%20361%20runs%20in%20seven%20innings%20and%20Dinesh%20Karthik%20has%20been%20enjoying%20a%20fine%20season%20for%20the%20team%20as%20a%20finisher%20but%20they%20have%20been%20completely%20overshadowed%20by%20RCB's%20underperforming%20bowling%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20did%20they%20say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20tough%2C%20we%20tried%20quite%20a%20few%20things%2C%20a%20few%20different%20things%2C%20and%20they%20weren't%20quite%20working.%20So%20it's%20a%20sign%20of%20confidence%20in%20the%20other%20group.%20When%20your%20confidence%20is%20low%2C%20there's%20nowhere%20to%20hide%20in%20the%20game.%26quot%3B%20du%20Plessis%20said%20after%20the%20loss%20against%20SRH.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20the%20game%20but%20I%20was%20really%20proud%20of%20the%20way%20we%20fought.%20It%20was%20really%20a%20night%20in%20the%20field%20of%20course.%20We%20will%20have%20a%20think%2C%20we%20will%20come%20back%20stronger%2C%20it's%20obviously%20knockout%20time.%20Every%20game%20is%20like%20a%20semi-final%20game%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%20RCB%20head%20coach%20Andy%20Flower%20looked%20optimistic%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%20chat%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20can%20RCB%20still%20qualify%20for%20IPL%20playoffs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERCB%2C%20as%20their%20head%20coach%20Andy%20Flower%20pointed%20out%2C%20need%20to%20treat%20every%20game%20from%20here%20as%20a%20knockout.%20RCB%20need%20to%20win%20their%20next%20seven%20matches%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20get%20to%2016%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%2016%20points%20might%20not%20prove%20enough%20if%20they%20are%20tied%20with%20one%20or%20more%20teams%20on%20the%20points%20table%20as%20their%20Net%20Run%20Rate%20has%20taken%20a%20beating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhenever%20the%20IPL%20had%20eight%20or%20more%20teams%20(in%202011%2C%202012%2C%202013%2C%202022%2C%202023)%2C%2016%20points%20have%20been%20the%20minimum%20to%20make%20the%20playoffs.%20The%20Royals%20Challengers%20have%20to%20win%20all%20their%20next%20seven%20fixtures%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20playoffs%20race%20and%20will%20also%20need%20other%20struggling%20teams%20like%20Delhi%20Capitals%2C%20Punjab%20Kings%2C%20and%20Mumbai%20Indians%20to%20lose%20as%20many%20matches%20as%20possible.%20But%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20smooth%20sailing%20for%20them%20as%20they%20will%20face%20four%20former%20IPL%20champions%20in%20their%20upcoming%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20matches%2C%20RCB's%20bowlers%20Mohammed%20Siraj%2C%20Reece%20Topley%2C%20Lockie%20Ferguson%2C%20Vyshak%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20Yash%20Dayal%2C%20Alzarri%20Joseph%20and%20others%20need%20to%20perform.%20They%20need%20to%20bounce%20back%20with%20a%20good%20economy%20and%20start%20picking%20up%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20need%20their%20overseas%20players%20like%20Cameron%20Green%2C%20Alzarri%20Joseph%2C%20Reece%20Topley%2C%20and%20Lockie%20Ferguson%20to%20deliver%20the%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERCB%20made%20a%20comeback%20in%20the%20past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERCB%20were%20languishing%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20points%20table%20after%20winning%20only%20one%20out%20of%20their%20first%20five%20matches%20in%20IPL%202009.%20However%2C%20they%20won%20seven%20of%20their%20next%20nine%20to%20reach%20the%20semi-finals%20and%20eventually%20the%20final.%20However%2C%20the%20Anil%20Kumble-led%20side%20was%20not%20able%20to%20win%20the%20title%20as%20they%20lost%20to%20the%20now-defunct%20Deccan%20Chargers%20in%20Johannesburg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERCB's%20remaining%20fixtures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApril%2021%2C%20Sunday%3A%20KKR%20v%2