20%26quot%3BAnd%20even%20despite%20this%20latest%20statement%2C%20he's%20still%20casting%20doubt%20on%20the%20election%20in%20general.%20That's%20been%20his%20rhetoric%20for%20years%20at%20this%20point%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-told-fans-new-hampshire-they-dont-have-to-vote-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eundermine%20democracy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20especially%20undermine%20American's%20faith%20in%20the%20democratic%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Trump%20loses%2C%20he's%20going%20to%20lie%20about%20it%20like%20he%20did%20in%202020.%20And%20if%20he%20wins%2C%20he%20will%20probably%20still%20lie%20about%20it%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0like%20he%20did%20in%202016%20when%20he%20claimed%20millions%20of%20people%20voted%20illegally%20in%20California%2C%20and%20claiming%20he%20actually%20won%20California%2C%26quot%3B%20Grossman%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20winning%20the%20election%2C%20he%20couldn't%20help%20himself%20with%20lying%20like%20that%2C%20so%20I%20expect%20that%20he%20will%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-backs-absentee-ballots-his-supporters-lost-faith-system-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713664219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6624343b83c8ec6e15306091%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-backs-absentee-ballots-his-supporters-lost-faith-system-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20said%20on%20Truth%20Social%20that%20absentee%20and%20early%20voting%20are%20%26quot%3Bgood%20options%26quot%3B%20for%20Republicans%20after%20years%20of%20sowing%20doubt%20about%20the%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww