C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20ANI%2C%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20question%20of%20merging%20our%20party%20with%20any%20other%20party.%20Categorically%2C%20I%20am%20telling%20you.%20There%20is%20no%20question.%20If%20the%20BJP%20treats%20us%20well%20and%20everything%20goes%20smoothly%2C%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20JDS%20being%20absorbed%20into%20the%20BJP.%20We%20will%20work%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20tell%20Siddaramaiah%20that%20even%20if%20100%20Siddaramaiahs%20come%20against%20us%2C%20they%20can't%20do%20anything%20to%20our%20party.%20They%20can't%20damage%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20back%20in%20time%2C%20in%202006%2C%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20rebelled%20and%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20JD(S)-Congress%20coalition%20with%2042%20MLAs%2C%20reportedly%20against%20the%20wishes%20of%20his%20father%2C%20former%20PM%20and%20JD(S)%20patriarch%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda%2C%20citing%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20party%2C%20and%20formed%20the%20government%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20asked%20whether%20inviting%20Deve%20Gowda%20to%20the%20''Pran%20Pratishtha''%20ceremony%20can%20be%20considered%20a%20personal%20connection%20between%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Deva%20Gowda%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20BJP-JD(S)%20alliance.%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20elaborated%20on%20the%20dynamics%20between%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Deve%20Gowda%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%20entered%20national%20politics%2C%20at%20that%20time%20Deve%20Gowda%20was%20one%20of%20the%20main%20critics%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20national%20entry.%20Then%2C%20despite%20whatever%20he%20said%20at%20that%20time%2C%20after%20Modi%20Ji%20became%20PM%2C%20he%20went%20to%20meet%20him.%20Deve%20Gowda%20ji%20wanted%20to%20resign%20from%20his%20MP%20constituency%2C%20but%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%20advised%20him%20that%20his%20advice%20was%20required%20and%20he%20must%20continue%20in%20parliament.%20This%20is%20the%20respect%20shown%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20Deve%20Gowda%20ji.%20After%20assuming%20the%20role%20of%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20they%20met%20several%20times%2C%20and%20each%20time%20the%20PM%20showed%20respect%20to%20Deve%20Gowda%20ji%20and%20sought%20his%20advice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20discussed%20Deve%20Gowda's%20political%20journey.%20%26quot%3BIn%202018%20Deve%20Gowda%20ji%20joined%20hands%20with%20Congress.%20Throughout%20his%20career%20of%2060-62%20years%2C%20he%20has%20always%20aligned%20with%20secular%20forces.%20By%20using%20regional%20parties%2C%20Congress%20has%20destroyed%20several%20regional%20parties.%20Congress%20has%20humiliated%20Deve%20Gowda%20ji%20in%20several%20ways.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%201995%2C%20when%20this%20United%20Front%20supported%20Deve%20Gowda%20Ji%20as%20a%20PM%20candidate%2C%20they%20(the%20Congress)%20did%20not.%20When%20they%20removed%20him%2C%20they%20had%20no%20reason%20at%20all.%20Even%20at%20that%20time%2C%20he%20also%20supported%20Inder%20Kumar%20Gujral.%20In%202004%2C%20again%2C%20they%20ditched%20Deve%20Gowda%20Ji.%20That%20time%20also%2C%20he%20respected%20Congress%2C%20even%20though%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20Arun%20Jaitley%20met%20him%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20BjP.%20Deve%20Gowda%20ji%20rejected%20it.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20he%20also%20joined%20hands%20with%20Congress%20and%20after%20joining%2C%20he%20watched%20how%20they%20treated%20him%20for%2020%20months.%20Even%20at%20that%20time%2C%20the%20health%20of%20Deve%20Gowda%20Ji%20deteriorated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20in%202009%2C%20he%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20third%20front.%20That%20is%20a%20different%20issue.%20Then%2C%20even%20after%20Deve%20Gowda%20ji%20handed%20over%20the%20power%20to%20the%20BJP%20at%20that%20time%20again%2C%20his%20Congress%20friend%20wanted%20to%20split%20our%20party.%20Continuously%2C%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20destroy%20our%20party.%20Even%20after%20this%2C%20Deve%20Gowda%20Ji%20joined%20hands%20with%20Congress%20only.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20why%20his%20party%20did%20that%2C%20he%20said%20he%20made%20several%20wrong%20decisions%20by%20trusting%20his%20Congress%20friends.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20totally%20against%20Congress.%20I%20know%20how%20they%20are%20going%20to%20treat%20us%20and%20how%20they%20treated%20me%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20at%20the%20Congress'%20remark%20where%20it%20slammed%20the%20JD%20(S)%20for%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20NDA%20and%20opined%20that%20the%20party%20should%20write%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20drop%20the%20word%20'secular'%20from%20their%20party's%20name%2C%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20meaning%20of%20secularism%3F%20I%20wanted%20to%20question%20the%20Congress.%20Every%20day%20they%20are%20misusing%20the%20caste%20composition%3B%20they%20are%20using%20the%20caste%20composition%20and%20they%20wanted%20to%20get%20benefit%20from%20it%20for%20their%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20me%2C%20there%20is%20no%20meaning%20to%20secularism%20or%20communalism.%20For%20example%2C%20let's%20talk%20about%20DMK.%20They%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20Centre%2C%20with%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%20Whatever%20the%20reason%20was%2C%20they%20took%20the%20decision%20in%20their%20own%20interest%2C%20not%20for%20secularism%20or%20communalism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713663780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F8924j0d8_hd-kumaraswamy_625x300_05_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-question-h