quot%3Bdangerous%20escalation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20would%20%26quot%3Btranslate%20into%20thousands%20of%20Palestinian%20casualties%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20said%20Nabil%20Abu%20Rudeina%2C%20spokesman%20for%20Palestinian%20president%20Mahmud%20Abbas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran%20plays%20down%20Israel%20attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Iran%20launched%20more%20than%20300%20missiles%20and%20drones%20a%20week%20ago%20in%20Tehran's%20first-ever%20direct%20attack%20on%20Israeli%20territory%2C%20Israel%20had%20warned%20it%20would%20hit%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Iran%20attack%20was%20itself%20in%20retaliation%20for%20an%20air%20strike%20--%20widely%20blamed%20on%20Israel%20--%20that%20levelled%20the%20Iranian%20consulate%20in%20Damascus%20and%20killed%20seven%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20on%20April%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20retaliation%20appeared%20to%20come%20on%20Friday%2C%20when%20Iranian%20media%20reported%20blasts%20in%20the%20central%20province%20of%20Isfahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFars%20news%20agency%20reported%20%26quot%3Bthree%20explosions%26quot%3B%20close%20to%20Qahjavarestan%2C%20near%20Isfahan%20airport%20and%20the%208th%20Shekari%20army%20airbase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%20last%20night%20was%20no%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20Iranian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Hossein%20Amir-Abdollahian%20told%20NBC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20flight%20of%20two%20or%20three%20quadcopters%2C%20which%20are%20at%20the%20level%20of%20toys%20that%20our%20children%20use%20in%20Iran%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20there%20is%20no%20new%20adventure%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Israeli%20regime%20against%20Iran's%20interests%2C%20we%20will%20have%20no%20response.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Israeli%20comment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20officials%20have%20made%20no%20public%20comment%20on%20what%20--%20according%20to%20a%20senior%20US%20congressional%20source%20who%20spoke%20to%20AFP%20--%20were%20retaliatory%20Israeli%20strikes%20against%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20tensions%20rose%20after%20the%20attack%20on%20Iran's%20consulate%2C%20violence%20involving%20Iran-backed%20groups%20had%20already%20been%20surging%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%20since%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20Gaza%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20in%20Iraq%20said%20one%20person%20was%20killed%20and%20eight%20wounded%20in%20an%20explosion%20at%20a%20military%20base%20south%20of%20Baghdad%20housing%20pro-Iranian%20armed%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20immediate%20claim%20of%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah%20group%20said%20three%20of%20its%20fighters%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20in%20south%20Lebanon%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hamas%20ally%20has%20exchanged%20near-daily%20cross-border%20fire%20with%20the%20Israeli%20army%20since%20the%20Gaza%20war%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20has%20also%20flared%20in%20the%20other%20occupied%20Palestinian%20territory%2C%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20Red%20Crescent%20said%20at%20least%2014%20people%20had%20been%20killed%20during%20a%2040-hour%20Israeli%20raid%20on%20a%20refugee%20camp%20in%20the%20northern%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20said%20it%20killed%2010%20%26quot%3Bmilitants%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20raid%20on%20Nur%20Shams%20camp.%20The%20Palestinian%20health%20ministry%20said%2011%20people%20were%20wounded%2C%20including%20a%20paramedic%20who%20was%20shot%20trying%20to%20reach%20earlier%20casualties%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENine%20members%20of%20one%20family%20killed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20faced%20increasing%20global%20opposition%20over%20its%20military%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20has%20reduced%20vast%20areas%20of%20the%20besieged%20Palestinian%20territory%20to%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIranian%20political%20expert%20Hamid%20Gholamzadeh%20said%20that%20Netanyahu%20--%20who%20is%20under%20pressure%20over%20the%20civilian%20toll%20--%20needs%20%26quot%3Bfurther%20escalation%20and%20another%20war%20to%20distract%20the%20world%20attention%26quot%3B%20away%20from%20suffering%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20particular%20fears%20about%20Israel's%20intention%20to%20send%20troops%20into%20the%20southernmost%20city%20of%20Rafah%2C%20where%20most%20of%20the%20population%20is%20now%20sheltering%2C%20having%20fled%20violence%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20ministers%20of%20the%20G7%20group%20of%20developed%20economies%20meeting%20in%20Italy%20on%20Friday%2C%20said%20they%20opposed%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-scale%20military%20operation%20in%20Rafah%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bcatastrophic%20consequences%26quot%3B%20for%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20without%20a%20full%20operation%2C%20the%20city%20has%20been%20under%20regular%20bombardment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Gaza's%20Civil%20Defence%20agency%20said%20several%20areas%20of%20Rafah%20had%20been%20hit%20overnight%2C%20including%20one%20Israeli%20strike%20that%20killed%20nine%20members%20of%20a%20family%20including%20six%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20was%20triggered%20by%20a%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20that%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%201%2C170%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20based%20on%20Israeli%20official%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20responded%20with%20a%20retaliatory%20offensive%20that%20has%20killed%20at%20least%2034%2C049%20people%20in%20Gaza%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20territory's%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFamine%20fears%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20it%20had%20struck%20dozens%20of%20militant%20targets%20over%20the%20past%20day%2C%20including%20the%20site%20in%20north%20Gaza%20from%20which%20a%20rocket%20was%20fired%20into%20the%20Israeli%20city%20of%20Sderot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20in%20the%20central%20Nuseirat%20refugee%20camp%20said%20the%20Israeli%20army%20had%20told%20them%20to%20evacuate%20one%20home%2C%20then%20several%20were%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20instruct%20us%20to%20evacuate%20and%20return%20later%2C%20but%20where%20do%20we%20go%20back%3F%20To%20ruins%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20resident%20Abu%20Ibrahim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20UN%20report%20on%20Friday%20said%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%20obstacles%26quot%3B%20continued%20to%20impede%20delivery%20of%20urgently%20needed%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20some%20recent%20aid%20convoys%20reaching%20Gaza%2C%20the%20World%20Food%20Programme%20cited%20%26quot%3Bthe%20real%20possibility%20of%20famine%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20north.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20seal%20a%20long-sought-after%20truce%20have%20stalled%2C%20according%20to%20mediator%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurkish%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%2C%20a%20staunch%20critic%20of%20Israel's%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20met%20with%20Qatar-based%20Hamas%20leader%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20on%20Saturday%2C%20calling%20for%20unity%20among%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Washington%20vetoed%20a%20Palestinian%20bid%20to%20become%20a%20full%20UN%20member%20state%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20president%20Mahmud%20Abbas%20said%20his%20West%20Bank-based%20Palestinian%20Authority%20would%20%26quot%3Breconsider%26quot%3B%20its%20relationship%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20it%20was%20summoning%20the%20ambassadors%20of%20the%2012%20countries%20that%20voted%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20bid%20%26quot%3Bfor%20a%20protest%20talk%26quot%3B%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%