th%20in%20Hubballi%20on%20Thursday%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20devastating%20killing%20of%20four%20members%20of%20the%20Bakale%20family%20in%20Gadag%20early%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22MANUAIYAPPA%20KANATHANDA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fgirls-murder-turns-law-order-into-major-poll-issue-in-karnataka%2Farticleshow%2F109465231.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22People%20Above%2065%20Can%20Also%20Buy%20Health%20Insurance%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Insurance%20Regulatory%20and%20Development%20Authority%20of%20India%20(IRDAI)%20has%20removed%20the%20age%20cap%20on%20buying%20health%20insurance%20policies%2C%20effective%20from%20April%201%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20individuals%20were%20restricted%20to%20purchasing%20new%20insurance%20policies%20only%20until%20the%20age%20of%2065.%20However%2C%20after%20the%20recent%20changes%20that%20have%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20April%2001%2C%202024%2C%20anyone%2C%20regardless%20of%20age%2C%20is%20eligible%20to%20purchase%20a%20new%20health%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInsurers%20shall%20ensure%20that%20they%20offer%20health%20insurance%20products%20to%20cater%20to%20all%20age%20groups.%20Insurers%20may%20design%20products%20specifically%20for%20senior%20citizens%2C%20students%2C%20children%2C%20maternity%2C%20and%20any%20other%20group%20as%20specified%20by%20the%20Competent%20Authority%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20IRDAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20by%20the%20insurance%20regulatory%20body%20aims%20to%20create%20a%20more%20inclusive%20healthcare%20ecosystem%20in%20India%20and%20to%20encourage%20insurance%20provider%20companies%20to%20diversify%20their%20product%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIRDAI%20has%20also%20instructed%20health%20insurance%20providers%20to%20introduce%20tailored%20policies%20for%20specific%20demographics%2C%20such%20as%20senior%20citizens%2C%20and%20establish%20dedicated%20channels%20for%20handling%20their%20claims%20and%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20welcome%20change%20since%20it%20now%20opens%20Avenue%20for%20people%20above%2065%20to%20seek%20health%20cover.%20Insurers%20based%20on%20their%20Board%20approved%20Underwriting%20guidelines%20can%20cover%20people%20above%2065.%20The%20coverage%20is%20subject%20to%20offer%20and%20acceptance%20between%20the%20Insured%20and%20Insurer%20based%20on%20affordability%20for%20the%20senior%20citizens%20and%20viability%20for%20Insurers.%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20Industry%20Expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20recent%20notification%2C%20the%20insurers%20are%20now%20also%20prohibited%20from%20refusing%20to%20issue%20policies%20to%20individuals%20with%20severe%20medical%20conditions%20like%20cancer%2C%20heart%20or%20renal%20failure%2C%20and%20AIDS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20notification%2C%20IRDAI%20has%20decreased%20the%20health%20insurance%20waiting%20period%20from%2048%20months%20to%2036%20months.%20According%20to%20the%20insurance%20regulator%2C%20all%20pre-existing%20conditions%20should%20be%20covered%20after%2036%20months%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20the%20policyholder%20disclosed%20them%20initially%20or%20not.%20Put%20simply%2C%20health%20insurers%20are%20prohibited%20from%20rejecting%20claims%20based%20on%20pre-existing%20conditions%20after%20these%2036%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20insurance%20companies%20are%20barred%20from%20introducing%20indemnity-based%20health%20policies%2C%20which%20compensate%20for%20hospital%20expenses.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20only%20permitted%20to%20provide%20benefit-based%20policies%2C%20offering%20fixed%20costs%20upon%20the%20occurrence%20of%20a%20covered%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndi