of%20the%20partisan%20squabbling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20request%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20some%20%248%20billion%20would%20be%20used%20to%20counter%20China%20through%20investment%20in%20submarine%20infrastructure%20and%20boosting%20competition%20with%20Beijing%20on%20projects%20built%20in%20developing%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20billion%20dollars%20would%20be%20devoted%20to%20weapons%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexternal-interference-cannot-stop-china-taiwan-unification-xi-jinping-5412891%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaiwan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20self-ruled%20island%20that%20is%20claimed%20by%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20provision%20would%20force%20TikTok%20to%20divest%20from%20its%20Chinese%20parent%20company%20ByteDance%20or%20face%20a%20nationwide%20ban%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20where%20it%20has%20around%20170%20million%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWestern%20officials%20have%20voiced%20alarm%20over%20the%20popularity%20of%20TikTok%20with%20young%20people%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20is%20subservient%20to%20Beijing%20and%20a%20conduit%20to%20spread%20propaganda%20--%20claims%20denied%20by%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bstrongly%20supports%26quot%3B%20the%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20been%20the%20chief%20military%20backer%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20its%20war%20against%20Russia%2C%20but%20Congress%20has%20not%20approved%20large-scale%20funding%20for%20its%20ally%20for%20nearly%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20mainly%20because%20of%20the%20bickering%20across%20the%20political%20aisle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-joe-bidens-hometown-produces-war-machinery-for-ukraine-5459487%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20in%20Congress%20have