as%20going%20to%20make%20this%20video%2C%20but%20I%20think%20it's%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunni%20says%20at%20the%20start%20of%20her%20TikTok%20video%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F04%2F17%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fabortion-tiktok-videos.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20video%20I%20was%20looking%20for.%20I%20was%20like%20'what's%20going%20to%20go%20on%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESunni's%20video%2C%20which%20received%20over%20400%2C000%20views%2C%20details%20her%20experience%20with%20mifepristone.%20The%20video%20attracted%20attention%20from%20anti-abortion%20groups.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40justsunni%2Fvideo%2F7308182699393518890%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProtect%20Life%20Michigan%3C%2Fa%3E%20responded%20directly%20to%20the%20video%20on%20TikTok%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bheartbreaking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Nall%2C%20founder%20of%20abortion%20access%20nonprofit%20Ineeda%2C%20told%20The%20Times%20that%20%26quot%3Bmore%20and%20more%20people%20are%20going%20online%26quot%3B%20with%20questions%20about%20abortion%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20chaos%20and%20the%20confusion%20and%20the%20stigma%26quot%3B%20of%20abortion%20bans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Jennifer%20Lincoln%2C%20an%20OBGYN%20who%20shares%20women's%20health%20information%20on%20TikTok%2C%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40drjenniferlincoln%2Fvideo%2F7270609221719215402%3F_t%3D8ldi3UhSSOU%26_r%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it's%20important%20for%20other%20women%20to%20show%20their%20experience%20with%20medication%20abortions%20for%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShes%20fantastic%20for%20doing%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Lincoln%20says.%20%26quot%3BShe%20showed%20what%20it%20was%20like%2C%20and%20in%20doing%20that%2C%20she's%20normalizing%20it.%20She's%20de-stig