%20uses%20to%20strike%20us%20are%20out%20of%20range%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20ramped%20up%20its%20attack%20on%20Kharkiv%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20bombarding%20the%20city%20with%20missiles%2C%20guided%20bombs%2C%20and%20drones%20in%20what%20officials%20believe%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20cut%20the%20city%20off%20from%20supplies%20and%20force%20the%20evacuation%20of%20civilians%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-04-16%2Frussia-is-trying-to-force-ukrainians-to-abandon-their-second-biggest-city%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20citing%20unnamed%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20commander%20in%20chief%20of%20Ukraine's%20armed%20forces%2C%20Oleksandr%20Syrskyi%2C%20told%20Ukrainian%20news%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-assault-ukraine-2nd-city-cant-be-ruled-out-commander-2024-3%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOleksandr%2520Syrskyi%2520said%2520Ukraine%2520was%2Cthe%2520country%2527s%2520second%252Dlargest%2520city.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUkrinform%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20could%20not%20ignore%20reports%20about%20Russia's%20plans%20to%20attack%20Kharkiv%20and%20that%20his%20troops%20were%20preparing%20for%20such%20an%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20carrying%20out%20a%20whole%20complex%20of%20works%20on%20the%20fortification%20of%20territories%20and%20positions%2C%20installing%20a%20complex%20system%20of%20fences%2C%20and%20planning%20the%20use%20of%20our%20troops%20in%20the%20event%20of%20such%20actions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutin%20has%20wanted%20to%20take%20Kharkiv%20since%20the%20start%20of%20Russia's%20full-scale%20invasion%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20has%20symbolic%20as%20well%20as%20strategic%20value%20for%20the%20Russian%20president%2C%20as%20it%20has%20a%20majority%20Russian-speaking%20population%20and%20was%20the%20first%20capi