ing%20verdict%20was%20a%20major%20news%20item%20at%20the%20time%2C%20mentioned%20in%20everything%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjon-stewart-jokes-about-robert-durst-on-daily-show-in-2003-2015-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJon%20Stewart%20monologue%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnl-robert-durst-sketch-2003-2015-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSaturday%20Night%20Live%26quot%3B%20skit%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%2012%20years%20after%20his%20acquittal%2C%20Durst%2C%20who%20was%20the%20son%20of%20New%20York%20real%20estate%20mogul%20Seymour%20Durst%2C%20participated%20in%20filmmaker%20Andrew%20Jarecki's%20Emmy-winning%20docuseries%20%26quot%3BThe%20Jinx%3A%20The%20Life%20and%20Deaths%20of%20Robert%20Durst.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20series%2C%20which%20began%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vulture.com%2F2015%2F03%2Frobert-durst-timeline-life-and-crimes.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilming%20in%202010%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20investigated%20the%20disappearance%20of%20McCormack%20in%201982%20and%20the%20murders%20of%20Berman%20and%20Black%2C%20featuring%20re-enactments%2C%20archival%20footage%2C%20and%20interviews%20with%20Durst%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Jinx%26quot%3B%20wasn't%20just%20a%20hit%20TV%20show.%20It%20also%20sparked%20renewed%20interest%20in%20the%20three%20cases.%20Durst%20was%20finally%20indicted%20for%20Berman's%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robert%20Durst%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6622e73023b29110d301336e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERobert%20Durst%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Jinx.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20HBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20show's%20most%20infamous%20moment%2C%20in%20the%20final%20episode%2C%20Durst%20was%20seeming