0city%20of%20Shenzhen%20on%20February%2017%2C%202009.%20BYD%20Auto%20is%20pursuing%20a%20project%20to%20free%20cars%20from%20their%20century-old%20dependence%20on%20gasoline%20and%20next%20month%20will%20start%20delivering%20the%20F3DM%20--%20DM%20stands%20for%20%26quot%3Bdual%20mode%26quot%3B%20--%20which%20can%20go%20100%20kilometres%20(63%20miles)%20on%20its%20battery%2C%20or%20580%20kilometres%20(360%20miles)%20in%20hybrid%20mode%20with%20gasoline.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6622c2fa83c8ec6e15303ecb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222417%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20Parks%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBYD%20moved%20into%20the%20car%20business%20after%20buying%20Xi'an%20Tsinchuan%2C%20a%20failing%20state-owned%20automaker%20that%20was%20then%20an%20arm%20of%20defense%20contractor%20Norinco%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Farticle%2F3217091%2Fchina-ev-war-how-byd-grew-elon-musks-ridicule-berkshire-hathaways-ridiculous-us98-billion-success-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20South%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20launched%20its%20first%20car%20in%202005.%20The%20BYD%20F3%20was%20a%20compact%20sedan%20that%20resembled%20the%20Toyota%20Corolla.%20It%20sold%20for%20as%20little%20as%2040%2C000%20yuan%2C%20or%20about%20%245%2C850.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWarren%20Buffett%20was%20a%20key%20early%20booster.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224320%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wang%20Chuanfu%20(L)%2C%20the%20Chairman%20and%20President%20of%20BYD%2C%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20CEO%20Warren%20E.%20Buffett%20(2nd-R)%2C%20Vice-Chairman%20Charles%20Thomas%20Munger%20(2nd-R)%20and%20Bill%20Gates%20(R)%2C%20founder%20of%20Microsoft%20Inc.%2C%20attend%20a%20new%20product%20launching%20conference%20of%20BYD%20at%20China%20World%20Hotel%20on%20September%2029%2C%202010%20in%20