ly%20production%20by%20tripling%20the%20area%20under%20production.%20She%20also%20wants%20to%20try%20for%20two%20harvests%20in%20a%20year%2C%20while%20typically%20only%20one%20harvest%20is%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20advantage%20of%20growing%20saffron%20indoors%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubha%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20people%20leading%20the%20shift%20towards%20indoor%20agriculture%2C%20especially%20in%20saffron.%20Many%20farmers%20in%20Kashmir%20too%20are%20making%20this%20switch%2C%20as%20climate%20change%20has%20severely%20hampered%20their%20saffron%20production.%20A%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20states%20that%20the%20area%20under%20saffron%20cultivation%20in%20Kashmir%20has%20reduced%20from%205%2C707%20hectares%20in%201996%20to%201%2C116%20hectares%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-30-1713440381.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shubha%20is%20providing%20employment%20to%2020%20women%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-30-1713440381.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-30-1713440381-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-30-1713440381-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-30-1713440381-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-30-1713440381-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347653%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShubha%20is%20providing%20employment%20to%2020%20women%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndoor%20farming%20isn%E2%80%99t%20threatened%20by%20climate%20change%2C%20soil%20issues%20or%20developments%20nearby.%20It%20is%20essentially%20foolproof%20if%20one%20masters%20the%20art%20of%20maintaining%20the%20right%20temperature%20and%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20advantage%20is%20the%20space%20needed%20for%20cultivation.%20%E2%80%9CA%20farmer%20would%20typically%20sow%202%2C000%20kg%20of%20saffron%20in%201.5%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20while%20we%20are%20able%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20560%20square%20feet%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ankit%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubha%20wants%20to%20create%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338349%2Fhow-to-grow-saffron-with-aeroponics-online-classes-himachal-pradesh-solan-mushrooms%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaffron%20%E2%80%9Crevolution%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20help%20more%20people%20grow%20the%20spice%20indoors.%20Through%20her%20venture%2C%20she%20is%20currently%20providing%20employment%20to%20over%2020%20women%20in%20Mainpuri%2C%20as%20the%20process%20of%20growing%20saffron%20is%20laborious.%20Right%20from%20drying%20the%20bulbs%20to%20plucking%20each%20stigma%2C%20drying%2C%20and%20packing%20them%2C%20it%20requires%20careful%20and%20precise%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20women%20like%20Geeta%20Devi%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20dependable%20income.%20At%2040%20years%20old%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20a%20mother%20of%20five%20and%20the%20primary%20provider%20for%20her%20family.%20Previously%2C%20she%20laboured%20in%20the%20fields%20under%20the%20scorching%20sun%2C%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20Work%20was%20inconsistent%2C%20and%20income%20was%20meagre%2C%20she%20recalls.%20However%2C%20since%20joining%20Shubhavni%20Farms%20last%20July%2C%20her%20situation%20has%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20enjoy%20the%20work%20here%20and%20brought