0imagined%20that%20I%20would%20start%20a%20business%20one%20day.%20It%E2%80%99s%20beyond%20our%20wildest%20dreams%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKitabwalah%20also%20accepts%20book%20donations.%20If%20you%20wish%20to%20donate%20a%20book%20or%20buy%20one%2C%20you%20can%20do%20so%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkitabwalah.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713434211000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkitab2-1713419328.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347598%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20his%20struggles%20to%20find%20affordable%20second-hand%20books%2C%20Muzaffarpur-based%20Akshay%20Kashyap%20co-founded%20Kitabwalah%20with%20his%20friend%20Srijan%20Kumar.%20They%20have%20sold%20over%206%2C000%20books%20making%20Rs%208%20lakh%20within%20two%20years%2C%20and%20have%20secured%20funding%20under%20the%20Bihar%20Startup%20Policy%202022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A61%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347598%2Fkitabwalah-buy-second-hand-books-akshay-kashyap-srijan-kumar-ncert-icse-cbse-iit-jee-muzaffarpur-bihar%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98There%20Are%202%20Ways%20Ahead%E2%80%99%3A%20IAS%20Officer%E2%80%99s%20Message%20For%20UPSC%20CSE%20Aspirants%20Who%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Make%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Ctrl%20%2B%20F%E2%80%99%20is%20probably%20the%20most%20dreadful%20combination%20on%20the%20keyboard%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347513%2Fupsc-cse-result-kunal-virulkar-no-selection-x-twitter-viral-tweet-trending%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20aspirant.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20announced%20the%20result%20of%20the%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20(CSE)%202023%20on%2016%20April.%20Thousands%20of%20aspirants%20looked%20for%20their%20names%20on%20the%20final%20list%2C%20and%20while%20the%20ones%20who%20found%20it%20rejoiced%2C%20the%20ones%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20felt%20dejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20cope%20with%20this%20dejection%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%20Jitin%20Yadav%20shared%20a%20message%20of%20hope%20and%20how%20to%20handle%20failure%20on%20X.%20Titled%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20ones%20who%20did%20not%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20list%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20gave%20his%20own%20example%20of%20what%20he%20did%20when%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20find%20his%20name%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Choly%20pdf%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20message%20to%20everyone%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20is%3A%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20give%20up.%20Never.%20Be%20proud%20that%20you%20have%20come%20this%20far.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJitin%20recalls%20sitting%20in%20his%20Gurugram%20house%2C%20heart%20pounding%2C%20as%20he%20impatiently%20checked%20the%20UPSC%20website%20multiple%20times%20to%20see%20if%20the%20result%20was%20out.%20Finally%2C%20as%20the%20results%20were%20declared%2C%20he%20downloaded%20the%20million-dollar%20final%20list%20and%20checked%20it%20thrice%20for%20his%20name.%20He%20even%20did%20%E2%80%98Ctrl%20%2B%20F%E2%80%99%20with%20trembling%20hands%2C%20confirming%20that%20he%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20selected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20numb%20and%20confused%2C%20and%20thought%20%E2%80%98Why%20only%20me%3F%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20candid%20post%20that%20now%20has%20over%201.25%20lakh%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20came%20to%20the%20bureaucrat%E2%80%99s%20rescue%20that%20day.%20Jitin%20met%20his%20friend%20and%20received%20an%20important%20life%20lesson%2C%20which%20applies%20to%20everyone%20in%20a%20difficult%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhatever%20happens%2C%20happens%20for%20good%20only.%20We%20can%20only%20give%20our%20100%25.%20There%20are%20two%20ways%20ahead%20%E2%80%94%20one%20to%20be%20depressed%20and%20do%20nothing%2C%20other%20to%20immediately%20bounce%20back%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20and%20do%20what%20all%20past%20selected%20candidates%20have%20done%20who%20faced%20rejections%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20and%20author%20chose%20the%20second%20option%20and%20was%20selected%20in%20the%20next%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20also%20not%20necessary%20for%20everyone%20to%20continue%20on%20the%20same%20path%20as%20there%20are%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345398%2Ffree-upsc-coaching-mentorship-programme-delhi-former-irs-officer-ravi-kapoor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20options%20beyond%20UPSC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20such%20students%2C%20he%20advises%20taking%20a%20break%20and%20then%20figuring%20out%20a%20future%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBetter%20things%20are%20waiting%20for%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20bureaucrat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20the%20entire%20post%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-twitter%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20ones%20who%20did%20not%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20list.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20was%20at%20home%20in%20Gurgaon%20and%20got%20to%20know%20that%20result%20will%20come%20today.%20I%20checked%20UPSC%20website%20after%20every%2015%20minutes.%20Finally%20the%20link%20came%